description:
The CoronaCrisis is making life more difficult for those who live in large cities compared to those who have country homes. God is speaking to His people. “Out of the cities!” is His warning. Need help? Discover resources to help you and your family exit modern Sodoms, plus ways to help city dwellers, without living in their midst. PDF resource: https://www.whitehorsemedia.com/time-to-leave-cities
